{"tid":2360891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特區政府反駁四國外長聲明斥持雙重標準  對香港法治引以自豪","createTime":"2021-01-10T07:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T08:52:24.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"da21fda68582eceed1ec4ed499069c1cf55fbcf8","tid":2360891,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:37:47.000Z","msg":"特區政府說，某些海外政府官員，似乎提出持某種政治理念的人不應受法律制裁的言論，對此感到震驚，重申國安法或特區任何法律，對香港每一個人皆平等適用，無人可以凌駕法律之上，不論嫌疑人的政治背景，執法機關都有責任對違法行為採取行動，對香港法治引以自豪。<br />\n<br />\n發言人說，國安法與其他司法管轄區相類似的國家安全法律看齊，甚至更佳，其他司法管轄區的高級官員妄語詆譭港區國安法，明顯是持雙重標準，強調將違法者繩之於法是每個政府的責任，尤其涉及國家安全，認為履行這個對國家的責任應該得到國際社會充分尊重。"},{"pid":"9037c315b537c789897c3cdfbd9b261bcdca8f42","tid":2360891,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:40:30.000Z","msg":"大和田.gif"},{"pid":"e1e4386cafc2c30c4242e8c6717482eaacda8bb7","tid":2360891,"uid":39872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"令中共損失十萬兆美元係每個人嘅責任"},{"pid":"2727a92d4793fcedbaa4d0d6c8cca70caa82411c","tid":2360891,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:43:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tnimage.s3.hicloud.net.tw/photos/2020/10/14/1602641302-5f865d967a692.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftnimage.s3.hicloud.net.tw%2Fphotos%2F2020%2F10%2F14%2F1602641302-5f865d967a692.jpg&h=5f2fbfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7594aa3e21e4ae58d980b1868f3f8359181a161","tid":2360891,"uid":18477,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T07:47:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">特區任何法律，對香港每一個人皆平等適用</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n班objects都幾好嘢㗎喎<br />\n講呢句都可以唧都唔笑"},{"pid":"57a007ec4caed8bdeb867284b7c337c09b1676cc","tid":2360891,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f7594aa3e21e4ae58d980b1868f